column2: ALKAMAG – 9-Stage Mineral & Alkaline Water Filter
column3:
ALKAMAG is a 9-stage advanced water filtration system that turns tap water into clean, great-tasting, mineral-rich alkaline water—without electricity or complicated setup.

It removes chlorine, sediment, bad tastes, and chemical residues. Then, it enriches the water with essential minerals like calcium, magnesium, and potassium—which are important for hydration, energy, muscle function, and overall wellness.

The result? Better hydration, smoother taste, and long-term cost savings. No electricity. No plastic waste. Just clean, mineral-boosted water for your family, office, or business

 

Key Benefits

  • ✅ 9 stages of complete water filtration

  • ✅ Improves taste, smell, and clarity of water

  • ✅ Adds important minerals: calcium, magnesium, potassium

  • ✅ Supports daily hydration and natural body balance

  • ✅ Alkaline water (pH 7.2–9.0) helps neutralize acidic foods

  • ✅ No power needed – fully mechanical

  • ✅ Long filter life (1 year or 5000L per set)

  • ✅ Saves money – reduce bottled water purchases

  • ✅ Eco-friendly – less plastic, less waste

 

How ALKAMAG Works – 9 Filtration Stages

  1. Sediment Filter – Captures dirt, sand, and rust

  2. Granular Activated Carbon (GAC) – Removes chlorine and odors

  3. Carbon Block (CTO) – Filters out smaller chemicals and improves taste

  4. Ion Exchange Resin – Reduces water hardness (scale-causing minerals)

  5. Far Infrared Ceramic Balls – Helps water absorb more easily in the body

  6. Tourmaline Ceramic Balls – Adds negative ions and increases oxygen content

  7. Alkaline Mineral Balls – Boosts pH and adds healthy minerals

  8. Maifan Stone – Enhances water with trace minerals from natural rock

  9. Antibacterial Ceramic – Inhibits bacterial growth inside the filter unit

 

Why Minerals Matter

Minerals added by ALKAMAG support real health benefits:

  • Calcium – Supports strong bones, muscles, and nerve function

  • Magnesium – Helps with energy production and reduces fatigue

  • Potassium – Balances fluids and supports heart and muscle health

  • Alkalinity – Helps balance body acidity caused by stress, coffee, and processed food

This isn’t just filtered water—it’s water that works with your body.


Who It’s For

  • Households and families

  • Health-conscious individuals

  • Offices and co-working spaces

  • Gyms, wellness clinics, and yoga studios

  • Cafés, salons, and small businesses

  • Anyone who wants cleaner, better-tasting water without plastic waste

 

Certifications & Lab Testing

ALKAMAG has been tested and certified according to international safety and quality standards, ensuring it is safe, reliable, and suitable for everyday use:

  • ✅ NSF Standard (USA)

    • NSF/ANSI 42 – Tested for reduction of non-health-related contaminants (taste, odor, clarity)

    • NSF/ANSI 61 – Certified for safe materials in drinking water systems

     

  • ✅ AMS Laboratories – Australia

    Independently tested for 6 key factors by a food and pharmaceutical lab recognized by international regulatory bodies:

    1. Water Taste – Verified ability to filter chlorine and improve flavor

    2. Appearance – Tested for water clarity and color consistency

    3. Aquatic Growth Prevention – Ensures no microbial contamination from plastic filter parts

    4. Cytotoxicity – Passed toxicology testing; safe for human use

    5. Mutagenicity – Tested for absence of genetic mutation risks

    6. Heavy Metal Extraction – Confirmed to reduce harmful metals in water

     

  • ✅ AS/NZS 4020:2005 Standard

    Certified according to Australian and New Zealand standards for drinking water systems

 

 

Important Notes

  • This product is not a medical device.

  • It is not intended to diagnose, treat, or cure any health condition.

  • ALKAMAG is designed to improve water quality, taste, and daily hydration.

  • All components are certified safe for drinking water use.

column2: Transform Soil – Premium Organic Soil Enhancer (1 kg)

Transform Soil is a premium organic soil enhancer designed to restore damaged land, improve plant health, and increase crop yield — all without relying on harsh chemicals. Its advanced formula combines natural ingredients like humic acid, biochar, dolomite, seaweed extract, amino acids, and zeolite to transform poor soil into fertile, productive ground.

This product improves soil structure, balances pH, boosts microbial life, and helps plants absorb nutrients more efficiently. It reduces the need for chemical fertilizers, retains more moisture, and promotes strong root development — making it ideal for everything from home gardens to large-scale farms.

Benefits:

  • Restores and rehabilitates damaged or nutrient-depleted soil

  • Increases fertilizer efficiency and reduces usage

  • Stimulates root growth and improves nutrient absorption

  • Enhances plant immunity and resistance to stress

  • Boosts microbial activity and soil aeration

  • Balances soil acidity/alkalinity for optimal plant growth

  • Increases the size, weight, and quality of fruits and vegetables

 

Main Natural Components:

  • Humic Acid: Improves nutrient retention, soil structure, and energy absorption from sunlight

  • Biochar (Bio-Charcoal): Improves moisture retention and promotes microbial growth

  • Dolomite: Reduces soil acidity and adds calcium & magnesium

  • Zeolite: Prevents nutrient leaching and helps detoxify the soil

  • Seaweed Extract: Strengthens plant cells and supports healthy fruit development

  • Amino Acids & Vitamin B1: Boosts photosynthesis and plant recovery under stress

  • Phosphate: Helps hold nutrients in the soil for longer-lasting effect

 

Lab-Tested Results (Thailand Central Lab):

  • Phosphorus increased from 44.15 mg/kg to 94.29 mg/kg

  • Potassium increased from 46.14 mg/kg to 7,641.2 mg/kg

  • Soil moisture improved from 10.8% to 14.38%

  • Soil pH balanced from acidic to neutral (ideal for plant absorption)

How to Use:  

Choose any one of the following methods — all are effective:

    1. Water Mix:

      Dissolve 10–50 grams of Transform Soil in 20 liters of water and pour directly onto the soil or around the base of the plant.

    2. Dry Sprinkle:

      Apply 2 tablespoons of Transform Soil around each plant and water afterward. Works best on wet or moist soil.

    3. Fertilizer Booster:

      Mix 1 kilogram of Transform Soil with 50–100 kilograms of fertilizer or compost to boost nutrient absorption and soil improvement.

    4. Field Spray:

      Dissolve 1 kilogram of Transform Soil in 1,500–2,000 liters of water and spray over large areas (recommended for farms or wide planting zones).

When to Use:

Use during planting, fertilization, or recovery periods — and whenever the soil shows signs of damage, poor moisture retention, or nutrient loss. Suitable year-round for all types of crops: vegetables, fruits, ornamental plants, rice, sugarcane, potatoes, corn, and more.

Safe, eco-friendly, and lab-proven — Transform Soil is the smart way to get better crops, healthier soil, and stronger plants.
